{"type":"text","timestamp":1775879746952,"sessionID":"ses_28552bab1ffeJ4HLNls30M75Or","part":{"id":"prt_d7aae5604001F6MlPhPJtZ411e","messageID":"msg_d7aae47a8001RDq2XktGzpGJTj","sessionID":"ses_28552bab1ffeJ4HLNls30M75Or","type":"text","text":"## AR-030 — Helm Chart 模板与 Values\n\n### Completed ✓\n\n**Core Chart Structure:**\n- `Chart.yaml` - Chart metadata (apiVersion v1, name agentcube, version 0.1.0)\n- `values.yaml` - Configuration for Redis, Router, WorkloadManager, Volcano Scheduler\n- `crds/agentruntimes.yaml` - AgentRuntime CRD\n- `crds/codeinterpreters.yaml` - CodeInterpreter CRD with status subresource\n\n**Templates:**\n- `agentcube-router.yaml` - Deployment + Service with health probes, WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL\n- `workloadmanager.yaml` - Deployment + Service with Redis integration\n- `rbac/workloadmanager.yaml` - ServiceAccount + ClusterRole + ClusterRoleBinding\n- `rbac-router.yaml` - Conditional Router RBAC (controlled by `router.rbac.create`)\n- `volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml` - Optional Volcano Scheduler with ConfigMap\n\n**Tests (unittest):**\n- `agentcube-router_test.yaml` - 8 test scenarios\n- `workloadmanager_test.yaml` - 8 test scenarios\n- `rbac-router_test.yaml` - RBAC toggle tests\n- `workloadmanager-rbac_test.yaml` - WorkloadManager RBAC tests\n- `volcano-scheduler_test.yaml` - Volcano scheduler tests\n\n---\n\n### Deferred\n\n**Missing Files (per design.md/delta-spec.md):**\n- `.helmignore` - Packaging exclusion patterns\n- `templates/_helpers.tpl` - Template helper functions\n- `templates/redis-secret.yaml` - Redis password Secret (REDIS_PASSWORD currently uses values directly)\n\n**Design Spec Gaps:**\n- Chart.yaml missing: keywords, maintainers, home, sources fields\n- Router uses direct password value instead of Secret reference\n- No `router.config` field implementation in values.yaml\n- No multi-environment values files (values-dev.yaml, values-prod.yaml)\n\n**Open Questions from Spec (unresolved):**\n1. External Redis Operator integration\n2. Monitoring/logging (Prometheus, ServiceMonitor)\n3. Multi-cluster deployment support\n4. Ingress configuration\n5. Pod Disruption Budgets","time":{"start":1775879746949,"end":1775879746949}}}
